# =====================================================================
# CodeFlow Shell вЂ” environment variable example
# =====================================================================
# Copy this file to ONE of the following locations:
#
#   1. ~/.codeflow/v2/.env       (per-user; recommended for personal use)
#   2. ./.env                    (project-local; commit-proof via .gitignore)
#
# Both files are loaded in order; project-local overrides per-user.
# `process.env` itself overrides BOTH (use `set CURSOR_API_KEY=...` for
# one-shot runs).
#
# Only the keys whitelisted here are read вЂ” every other env var the shell
# sees is ignored, so you can keep these files small and audit-friendly.
# Reference: TASK-20260510-002-PM-to-DEV В§дё‰ P1 В§1 + codeflow-shell/src/config.ts
# =====================================================================

# в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ Cursor SDK в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
# Required for the real `CursorSdkAdapter` to fire. Without this key,
# the shell falls back to `InMemorySdkAdapter` (synthetic settle, no
# real LLM calls вЂ” good for smoke tests but `decision="needs_human"`).
# Get a key from: https://cursor.com/settings (Account в†’ API keys).
CURSOR_API_KEY=ck_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# Optional: per-call default model hint. Not yet wired to all 4 SDK
# methods in v0.2.0-alpha (see REPORT-20260510-002-DEV-to-PM В§е†із­–);
# recorded here for forward compat.
# CURSOR_DEFAULT_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4

# Optional: `local` (default) or `cloud`. Controls whether
# `Agent.list()` enumerates per-cwd local agents or cross-machine
# cloud agents.
# CURSOR_LIST_SCOPE=local

# в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ Mobile / Relay в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
# These activate the v0.2 P3 `RelayBridge` that connects the shell to
# the Mobile PWA over WebSocket. P3 is NOT shipped in v0.2.0-alpha
# (P1) вЂ” leaving these unset is the right thing for now.
# CODEFLOW_RELAY_URL=wss://ai.chedian.cc/codeflow/ws/
# CODEFLOW_ROOM_KEY=codeflow-replace-with-your-id
# CODEFLOW_RELAY_AUTOCONNECT=true

# в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ Data dir в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
# Where the shell keeps `agents.json`, `inbox/`, `reviews/`, etc.
# Defaults to `~/.codeflow/v2/`. Use this to point at a project-local
# directory for testing without polluting the user-level state.
# CODEFLOW_DATA_DIR=~/.codeflow/v2
